description:
Squidward was given the impossible task of training a group of monkeys to play "Sweet Victory" by David Glen Eisley and Bob Kulick at the annual Bubble Bowl. To his and Squilliam's surprise, what seemed impossible, was, indeed, possible and by God is it beautiful.

A video I made for Neverthink's 2nd Mini Meme Jam, where Neverthink Partners are given about a weekend to make a meme around 1 theme. This jam's theme was Monke.

Gorilla Drumming Greenscreen: https://youtu.be/-EtwyJJTyh8
